# keep reference dataset directory
# datasets/benchmarks/

Benchmark CSV files live here and are not committed.

Examples:

```text
i2p.csv
nudity.csv
LAION-COCO-NSFW-1000.csv
LAION-COCO-SFW-1000.csv
nudity-ring-a-bell.csv
```

Use this folder for prompt/evaluation CSVs, not image-mask training data.

